&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;It’s readable as plain text, so you can edit it in any editor and keep it in version control. Formatting is minimal: headings, lists, links, code blocks. That keeps the focus on what you’re saying instead of layout tweaks.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;]]&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>